&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Interested in joining our Talent Community? &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Perhaps, the right role for you is just around the corner. Feel free to submit your resume and we&#39;ll keep your resume ready for the right role.&amp;nbsp;Upwork has various exciting roles as our company continues to grow. If you didn&#39;t find a role currently open that fit your skill set, then please feel free to join our talent community. The Upwork Talent Community, will hold your resume and contact you as soon as a role opens that may fit your specific skills and career goals.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
