&lt;li&gt;Strategic Communication: Present insights and recommendations to marketing leadership, influencing growth strategy and prioritization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experimentation &amp;amp; Testing: Design, execute, and analyze A/B and incrementality tests. Define hypotheses, success metrics, and test duration, and conduct deep post-test analysis to inform decisions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive insights that improve conversion, engagement, and overall growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Data Extraction &amp;amp; Technical Analysis: Extract and analyze large datasets using SQL, Python, or R to support experimentation, user behavior analysis, and growth initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experimentation Tooling: Utilize platforms such as Statsig, Optimizely, VWO, or similar tools to implement and monitor experiments across experiences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;SEO Tooling: Leverage tools such as Google Search Console, SEMrush, Ahrefs, or similar to explore keyword performance and on-site engagement trends.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
